		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Back in February three friends and I rented an RV and spent some time touring Hokkaido on our skis. I have been super busy with an international move and ticking off items on my <em>"must do before leaving Japan"</em> list - hence the month plus delay in posting this trip report. As I write this I am sitting in Los Angeles enjoying some exquisite Mexican food, In-N-Out, and driving on highways that don't cost an arm and a leg - but I am missing my friends and this upcoming keiryu tenkara and sansai season, which is sure to be epic! If you can get to Japan this year <strong>DO IT</strong>!

[caption id="attachment_5491" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="wp-image-5491 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-first-tour-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> First tour (for me). Headed up Furanodake.[/caption]

<!--more-->

I am experimenting with a new format; heavy on photos and light on words - because as you know they say "pictures speak a thousand words". Here's a map of where we went... If you want more beta <a href="http://104.248.67.90/about/contact/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hit me up</a>.

<div style="text-align: center;"><iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1YYxEfs3hCwkF5JEASRi3C-Y_SIUqyUFa" width="640" height="480"></iframe></div>

<div></div>

<div>

[caption id="attachment_5522" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5522" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-my-son-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> The day of the trip, before I had to head to the airport I took my son to lunch. He got this for his "kids meal toy" - I thought it was fitting[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5496" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="wp-image-5496 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-dont-want-to-get-sick-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> As they say "when in Rome..." rocking the face mask on the way to the airport[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5497" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="wp-image-5497 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-headed-to-the-airport-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> Next stop Hokkaido, as I snapped this photo I was wondering if I would freeze to death or not[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5519" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="wp-image-5519 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-artsy-fartsy-1024x577.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="577" /> On the Keikyu Express to Haneda Airport[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5495" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5495" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-our-steed-for-the-week-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> Meeting the guys at the airport - next stop Furanodake[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5509" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="wp-image-5509 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-four-guys-one-RV-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> My friend Scott and our trusty steed.[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5518" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5518" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-parking-lot-for-furano-dake-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> As we pulled into the Furanodake parking lot someone was leaving - so we got front row parking![/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5517" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5517" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Best meal of the trip was a hole in the wall izakaya suggested to us by another hole in the wall sake shop owner! I love Japan[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5512" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5512" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-tomamu-at-night-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Tomamu Resort is legit, good food and an epic gear shop. "How much is the limit on my American Express again?"[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5513" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5513" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-where-is-the-plow-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" /> 45cm of snow on the road. Good thing we have a diesel 4x4[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5514" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5514" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-top-of-tomamu-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> If you think the front side of Tomamu is fun try the backside![/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5516" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5516" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-scott-the-abominable-snowman-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Yeti![/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5511" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5511" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-epic-locals-resort-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Getting ready for an epic day of inbound face shots![/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5510" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5510" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-fueling-up-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Seco Mart found only in Hokkaido has some great grub![/caption]

<div style="text-align: center;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/47dViTJjZx4" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<strong>A video compilation from our trip.</strong>

[caption id="attachment_5508" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5508" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-downtown-sapporo-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Downtown Sapporo is a must visit if you're in the area[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5507" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5507" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-lunch-break-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Lunch break on Furanodake with sketchy conditions[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5502" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5502" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-earning-the-turns-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Epic turns here we come[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5503" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="wp-image-5503 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-ice-sculptures-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Ich, Ni, San Cheesu - Kevin and I getting in on the tourist photo op action[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5504" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5504" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-japanese-curry-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Japanese curry[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5505" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5505" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-up-and-up-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Earning our turns[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5506" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5506" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-so-much-terrain-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> So much terrain! I need at least a week[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5501" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5501" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-man-that-sucked-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Bushwacking on skis through a boscage is really hard work, especially on the last day[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5500" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5500" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-just-a-bunch-of-dirtbags-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> After nearly a mile of ascending we were starving![/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5499" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5499" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-primo-parking-spot-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Horotachi is a small local resort with only one lift - and some fun albeit short runs[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5498" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="wp-image-5498 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-light-festival-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /> Our fearless leader Junpei enjoying the downtown Sapporo light festival after a delicious meal[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5492" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5492" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-god-hotdogs-and-rock-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> You gotta love Japlish[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5493" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5493" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-spiky-stick-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> This little guy looks pretty cute but his bigger brother and sisters aren't so cute...[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5494" align="aligncenter" width="768"]<img class="size-large wp-image-5494" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-sketchy-stream-crossing-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="1024" /> This is harder than it looks[/caption]

[caption id="attachment_5520" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<img class="wp-image-5520 size-large" src="http://104.248.67.90/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/hokkaido-japow-skiing-adventure-kiroro-tomamu-furanodake-horotachi-japan-lake-shikotsu-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" /> Sunset over Lake Shikotsu on the last day headed back to the airport[/caption]

</div>]]></content:encoded>
